articles.title: Prime Video Deploys AI Program to Raise Movie, TV Dialogue Volume
articles.description: You've almost certainly noticed in recent years that sometimes movies and TV shows have gotten incredibly hard to hear, prompting many to even use subtitles with everything they watch. A great expose on SlashFilm covers the topic and its causes for recent feature films, and now one streamer believes they've found a way to navigate the problem...kind of
